Minimal, säker fix i removeVessel (SystemCoordinator.js:495-498): hämta entryt och rensa timern innan delete, speglande re-arm-mönstret rad 354-356:
```
removeVessel(mmsi) {
  this.vesselCoordinationState.delete(mmsi);
  const debounceData = this.bridgeTextDebounce.get(mmsi);
  if (debounceData && debounceData.timer) {
    clearTimeout(debounceData.timer);
  }
  this.bridgeTextDebounce.delete(mmsi);
}
```
